        "body": "## Overview\r\n\r\nCloses #3036\r\nThis PR works on the Machine Translation Explanations notebook and core text masker to:\r\n\r\n-Fix a crash in shap.maskers.Text by handling missing offset_mapping from certain HuggingFace tokenizers.\r\n-Remove hardcoded GPU usage by replacing .cuda() with device-agnostic code (CPU/GPU compatible).\r\n-Add brief explanations and comments to improve readability.\r\n-Include version logging for reproducibility.\r\n-Ensure all notebook cells run cleanly end-to-end with outputs saved.\r\n<img width=\"1280\" height=\"448\" alt=\"PR1\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a164b376-d661-4850-97a2-f8ff87ec26de\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## Checklist\r\n\r\n- [x] All [pre-commit checks](https://pre-commit.com/#install) pass.\r\n- [ ] Unit tests added (if fixing a bug or adding a new feature)\r\n",
